---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Frais de Scolarite" lang="fr" description="Frais de scolarite et informations financieres pour Forest International School Paris">
  <!-- Hero Section with Image -->
  <section class="relative py-20 lg:py-32 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0">
      <img src="/images/campus.jpg" alt="Campus de Forest International School" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#1e3d29]/95 via-[#2d5a3d]/80 to-[#2d5a3d]/60"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="relative max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-2xl">
        <span class="inline-block px-4 py-2 bg-[#c9a962]/20 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-full text-[#c9a962] font-semibold text-sm mb-6 border border-[#c9a962]/30">Frais</span>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Frais de Scolarite</h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-white/90 leading-relaxed">
          Les frais de scolarite annuels couvrent le programme, les ressources pedagogiques, les livres, les activites en foret et les frais de fonctionnement. Des plans de paiement et des bourses sont disponibles sur evaluation financiere.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- New Starters Special Fee -->
  <section class="py-16 lg:py-24 bg-[#faf8f5]">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <span class="inline-block px-4 py-2 bg-[#c9a962]/20 rounded-full text-[#c9a962] font-semibold text-sm mb-4">Nouvelles Familles</span>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-[#1e3d29]">Nouveaux Inscrits 2025-2026</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mt-4 max-w-3xl mx-auto">Les nouvelles familles, s'inscrivant a FISP pour la premiere fois et payant elles-memes les frais de scolarite, beneficient d'un forfait unique tout compris.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-[#2d5a3d] to-[#1e3d29] rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-xl text-white">
          <div class="text-center mb-8">
            <span class="text-[#c9a962] text-sm font-semibold uppercase">Ages 2-12</span>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-2">Forfait Premiere Annee Tout Compris</h3>
          </div>

          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-8">
            <div class="bg-white/10 rounded-xl p-4 text-center">
              <p class="text-white/70 text-sm">Frais d'inscription</p>
              <p class="text-2xl font-bold">0 EUR</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white/10 rounded-xl p-4 text-center">
              <p class="text-white/70 text-sm">Frais de developpement</p>
              <p class="text-2xl font-bold">0 EUR</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white/10 rounded-xl p-4 text-center">
              <p class="text-white/70 text-sm">Frais de scolarite</p>
              <p class="text-2xl font-bold">12 500 EUR</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white/10 rounded-xl p-4 text-center">
              <p class="text-white/70 text-sm">Frais de cantine*</p>
              <p class="text-2xl font-bold">2 500 EUR</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="border-t border-white/20 pt-6 text-center">
            <p class="text-white/70 text-sm mb-2">Total Premiere Annee</p>
            <p class="text-5xl font-bold text-[#c9a962]">15 000 EUR</p>
          </div>

          <p class="text-white/60 text-sm mt-6 text-center">*Les frais de cantine comprennent les dejeuners et collations biologiques. Aucun frais pour les enfants apportant leur propre repas.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Annual Fees by Section -->
  <section class="py-16 lg:py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <span class="inline-block px-4 py-2 bg-[#2d5a3d]/10 rounded-full text-[#2d5a3d] font-semibold text-sm mb-4">2025-2026</span>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-[#1e3d29]">Frais Annuels</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mt-4 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Eleves de retour et inscriptions sponsorisees par l'employeur</p>
      </div>

      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <!-- Fee Table -->
        <div class="bg-[#faf8f5] rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg">
          <!-- Header -->
          <div class="grid grid-cols-6 gap-2 p-4 bg-[#2d5a3d] text-white text-sm font-semibold">
            <div class="col-span-1">Section</div>
            <div class="text-center">Reinscription</div>
            <div class="text-center">Developpement</div>
            <div class="text-center">Scolarite</div>
            <div class="text-center">Cantine**</div>
            <div class="text-center">Total Annuel</div>
          </div>

          <!-- Pre-School -->
          <div class="grid grid-cols-6 gap-2 p-4 border-b border-gray-200 items-center">
            <div class="col-span-1">
              <p class="font-bold text-[#1e3d29]">Pre-scolaire</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">2-3 ans</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <p class="font-semibold">350 EUR</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <p class="font-semibold">1 500 EUR</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <p class="font-semibold">12 500 EUR</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <p class="font-semibold">2 500 EUR</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <p class="font-bold text-[#2d5a3d] text-lg">16 850 EUR</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Early Years -->
          <div class="grid grid-cols-6 gap-2 p-4 border-b border-gray-200 items-center bg-white">
            <div class="col-span-1">
              <p class="font-bold text-[#1e3d29]">Maternelle</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">3-4 ans</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <p class="font-semibold">350 EUR</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <p class="font-semibold">1 500 EUR</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <p class="font-semibold">16 000 EUR</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <p class="font-semibold">2 500 EUR</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <p class="font-bold text-[#2d5a3d] text-lg">20 350 EUR</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Lower Primary -->
          <div class="grid grid-cols-6 gap-2 p-4 border-b border-gray-200 items-center">
            <div class="col-span-1">
              <p class="font-bold text-[#1e3d29]">Primaire Inferieur</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">5-7 ans</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <p class="font-semibold">350 EUR</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <p class="font-semibold">1 500 EUR</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <p class="font-semibold">17 500 EUR</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <p class="font-semibold">2 500 EUR</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <p class="font-bold text-[#2d5a3d] text-lg">21 850 EUR</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Upper Primary -->
          <div class="grid grid-cols-6 gap-2 p-4 items-center bg-white">
            <div class="col-span-1">
              <p class="font-bold text-[#1e3d29]">Primaire Superieur</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">8-12 ans</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <p class="font-semibold">350 EUR</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <p class="font-semibold">1 500 EUR</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <p class="font-semibold">19 000 EUR</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <p class="font-semibold">2 500 EUR</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <p class="font-bold text-[#2d5a3d] text-lg">23 350 EUR</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Notes -->
        <div class="mt-8 space-y-3 text-sm text-gray-600">
          <p><span class="font-semibold">*Frais couverts par l'employeur :</span> Factures au tarif plein, non remise, aligne sur les organisations internationales en France. Frais de developpement unique de 4 500 EUR applicable.</p>
          <p><span class="font-semibold">**Frais de cantine :</span> Comprend les dejeuners et collations biologiques. Aucun frais pour les enfants apportant leur propre repas.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Sibling Discounts -->
  <section class="py-16 lg:py-24 bg-[#faf8f5]">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <span class="inline-block px-4 py-2 bg-[#c9a962]/20 rounded-full text-[#c9a962] font-semibold text-sm mb-4">Avantages Famille</span>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-[#1e3d29]">Reductions Fratrie</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mt-4 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Les frais de scolarite annuels combines sont reduits pour les familles avec plusieurs enfants.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 text-center hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#2d5a3d] to-[#4a7c5c] rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">2</span>
            </div>
            <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-[#c9a962] mb-2">20%</div>
            <p class="text-gray-600 font-medium">Deuxieme Enfant</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 text-center hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#4a7c5c] to-[#2d5a3d] rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">3</span>
            </div>
            <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-[#c9a962] mb-2">25%</div>
            <p class="text-gray-600 font-medium">Troisieme Enfant</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 text-center hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#c9a962] to-[#d4b872] rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">4+</span>
            </div>
            <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-[#c9a962] mb-2">30%</div>
            <p class="text-gray-600 font-medium">Quatrieme Enfant+</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Additional Fees -->
  <section class="py-16 lg:py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <span class="inline-block px-4 py-2 bg-[#2d5a3d]/10 rounded-full text-[#2d5a3d] font-semibold text-sm mb-4">Options Supplementaires</span>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-[#1e3d29]">Frais Supplementaires</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <div class="bg-[#faf8f5] rounded-3xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden">
          <!-- Breakfast Club -->
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between p-6 border-b border-gray-200">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#c9a962] rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 3v1m0 16v1m9-9h-1M4 12H3m15.364 6.364l-.707-.707M6.343 6.343l-.707-.707m12.728 0l-.707.707M6.343 17.657l-.707.707"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-[#1e3d29]">Club du Petit-Dejeuner</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Lun-Ven 7h30-8h30</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-right">
              <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#2d5a3d]">12 EUR</span>
              <span class="text-gray-600 ml-1">par seance</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- After School Clubs -->
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between p-6 border-b border-gray-200">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#4a7c5c] rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-[#1e3d29]">Clubs Apres l'Ecole</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Lun-Ven 16h00-17h00</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-right">
              <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#2d5a3d]">17 EUR</span>
              <span class="text-gray-600 ml-1">par seance</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Bus Service -->
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between p-6 border-b border-gray-200">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#2d5a3d] rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 7h12m0 0l-4-4m4 4l-4 4m0 6H4m0 0l4 4m-4-4l4-4"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-[#1e3d29]">Service de Bus</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Service porte-a-porte</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-right">
              <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#2d5a3d]">4 850 - 9 850 EUR</span>
              <span class="text-gray-600 ml-1">/an</span>
              <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm">Selon la localisation</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Annual School Trip -->
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between p-6 border-b border-gray-200">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#8b7355] rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3.055 11H5a2 2 0 012 2v1a2 2 0 002 2 2 2 0 012 2v2.945M8 3.935V5.5A2.5 2.5 0 0010.5 8h.5a2 2 0 012 2 2 2 0 104 0 2 2 0 012-2h1.064M15 20.488V18a2 2 0 012-2h3.064M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-[#1e3d29]">Voyage Scolaire Annuel</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Un voyage par annee scolaire pour les eleves du primaire</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-right">
              <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#2d5a3d]">750 EUR</span>
              <span class="text-gray-600 ml-1">/an</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- SEN Support -->
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between p-6">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#6b8e7a] rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-[#1e3d29]">Accompagnement BEP (Besoins Educatifs Particuliers)</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Nous accueillons les enfants avec des besoins specifiques au cas par cas</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-right">
              <span class="text-gray-600">Demandez le document "Frais BEP"</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Financial Assistance -->
  <section class="py-16 lg:py-24 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#2d5a3d] to-[#1e3d29]">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <div class="flex justify-center mb-6">
        <img src="/images/inst_savio.avif" alt="SAVIO Education" class="h-16 bg-white rounded-lg p-2" />
      </div>
      <span class="inline-block px-4 py-2 bg-[#c9a962]/20 rounded-full text-[#c9a962] font-semibold text-sm mb-6 border border-[#c9a962]/30">Aide Financiere & Financement</span>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Bourse SAVIO Education</h2>
      <p class="text-white/80 text-lg mb-4 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Des plans de paiement echelonne sont disponibles sur demande.
      </p>
      <p class="text-white/80 text-lg mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Pour soutenir l'acces a notre mission educative, la Bourse SAVIO Education offre une remise sur les frais de scolarite selon l'eligibilite et la candidature.
      </p>
      <a href="/fr/contact" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 bg-white text-[#2d5a3d] font-bold rounded-full hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors shadow-lg">
        Contactez-nous pour plus de details
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
